Package: metapsyTools
Type: Package
Title: Several R Helper Functions For The "Metapsy" Database
Version: 0.3.0
Author: Mathias Harrer[cre], Paula Kuper[cre], Pim Cuijpers[aut]
Authors@R: c(
    person("Mathias", "Harrer", email = "mathias.h.harrer@gmail.com", role = "cre", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-7016-2687")),
    person("Paula", "Kuper", email = "paula.r.kuper@gmail.com", role = "aut"),
    person("Pim", "Cuijpers", email = "p.cuijpers@vu.nl", role = "aut", comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-5497-2743")))
Description: A companion R package for the metapsy database. It aims to faciliate calculation of meta effect sizes for the included trials. For this purpose, data can be checked and converted into the required format to calculate the effect sizes for all trials. It is then possible to run a meta- analysis over the output effect sizes. 
